title: Split Floorplan, perfect for roommates!! WiFi Included!
posting_body: ['Mike Miller', '| The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', 'Hwy 169, Anoka, MN', '$1,810/month', 'Bedrooms: 2   Bathrooms: 2 bath', 'Sq Footage 1050', 'Parking: 2 Dedicated', 'Pet Policy: Cats & Dogs OK', 'Deposit $500', 'Observe nature with the unsurpassed beauty of the trees, unruffled wildlife and acres of parkland as your neighbor.', 'Your lifestyle will flow with the serenity of the Mississippi River.', 'Fishing docks, picnic gazebos, walking trails, horseshoe pits and a private dog park are as close as your own backdoor.', 'We are also located only 1.5 miles from the new Northstar Light Rail so getting to Downtown Minneapolis just become even easier!', 'We are also pleased to announce we have installed WiFi through out the community!', 'The WiFi amenity will deliver Internet to your apartment free of charge.', 'We welcome your cats and your dogs.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'Community Features', 'Car wash', 'Soft water included', 'Cable Ready', 'Trash chutes/recycling', 'Basketball Court', 'BBQ Grilling Area', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Balcony/Patio on All Homes', 'High Speed Internet Available', 'Elevator in Building', 'Controlled Building Access', 'Close to Shopping, Restaurants and Downtown', 'Monitoring Cameras', 'Outdoor Pool', 'Community Room w/ Free WiFi', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Contact:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info']
